<h1 align=center style='text-align:center'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
18.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:华文中宋;font-weight:normal'>${evaluateUnit.evaluateunitname!""}</span></h1>

<h1 align=center style='text-align:center'><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
line-height:240%;font-family:华文中宋;font-weight:normal'>区域防突措施效果检验及瓦斯抽采效果达标评判报告</span></h1>

<p class=MsoTitle style='text-align:center'><span style='font-size:15.0pt;font-family:宋体'>第一章</span><span
style='font-size:15.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:15.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>概况</span></p>

<h2 style='margin-top:7.8pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:
0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:28.1pt;line-height:25.0pt'><a
name="_Toc410282987"><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>一、</span></a><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>基本概况</span></h2>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>位于<span lang=EN-US>${workFace.miningarea!""}</span><span style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>，工作面对应地面标高为<span lang=EN-US>+35.6</span>～<span
lang=EN-US>+37.2m</span>，工作面标高为<span lang=EN-US>-524.5</span>～<span lang=EN-US>-692.0m</span>，工作面北为大巷保护煤柱，南为<span
lang=EN-US>F40</span>断层保护煤柱，西为实体煤，东为<span lang=EN-US>DF4</span>断层保护煤柱。工作面对应地表为农田，工作面回采时由于地表塌陷对农田有一定的影响。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>本次评判范围为<span
lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span>Ⅱ段下部（即<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷为<span lang=EN-US>404G9</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>75m</span>至<span
lang=EN-US>404G6</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>29.4m</span>，<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷为<span
lang=EN-US>404P7</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>45m</span>至<span lang=EN-US>404P2</span>点内<span
lang=EN-US>45.6m</span>，及其对应的回采区域煤体）；<span lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span>Ⅱ段上部（</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>2404</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>上巷为<span lang=EN-US>404H10</span>点内<span
lang=EN-US>101m</span>至<span lang=EN-US>404H3</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>46m</span>，<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷为<span lang=EN-US>404G9</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>75m</span>至<span
lang=EN-US>404G5</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>38.7m</span></span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>，及其对应的回采区域煤体）。</span><span
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:华文中宋'> </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

<h2 style='margin-top:7.8pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:
0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:28.1pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>二、煤层赋存特征</span></h2>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:23.5pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>1.</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>煤厚及其稳定性</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:25.0pt'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>根据三维地震资料及</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>底抽巷施工钻孔见煤情况分析，</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>二</span><sub><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>2</span></sub><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>煤层赋存基本稳定，煤层厚度</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>2.2</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>～</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>3.0m</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>，平均</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>2.7m</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>。煤岩成分以镜煤为主，亮煤、暗煤次之。煤岩类型，以亮煤为主，属光亮型煤，断口为贝壳状，比重小，结构简单。煤层倾角</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>5</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>～</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>15</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>°，平均倾角</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>10°</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:23.5pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>2.</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>煤层结构</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>根据<span lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span></span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>底抽巷施工钻孔见煤情况</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>资料及掘进期间巷道实际揭露情况，<span lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span>Ⅱ段内二<sub><span
lang=EN-US>2</span></sub>煤层结构简单。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:23.5pt;line-height:26.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>3.</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>煤体结构</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>根据</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>三维地震</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>资料及掘进期间巷道实际揭露情况，工作面煤层顶板主要为</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>泥岩、粉砂岩，底板主要为泥岩、粉砂岩，围岩整体较稳定，局部裂隙发育</span><span
