<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'>2404</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷、<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷进风，<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>上巷回风。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'>1.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'>进风风流路线：地面新鲜风流→副井（主井）→<span
lang=EN-US>-702m</span>水平西翼轨道运输大巷（<span lang=EN-US>-702m</span>水平西翼胶带运输大巷）→<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷（<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷）→<span lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span>。</span></p>

<p class=New style='text-indent:27.55pt;line-height:25.0pt'><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>五、抽采系统</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><a
name="_Toc384991628"></a><a name="_Toc384991627"><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black'>顺和煤矿地面及风井底各设置一处抽采泵站，其中地面抽采泵站配备<span lang=EN-US>2</span>台<span
lang=EN-US>2BEC62</span>型水环式真空泵，抽采能力<span lang=EN-US>260m3/min</span>；井下抽采泵站配备<span
lang=EN-US>2</span>台<span lang=EN-US>2BE1505-1BG3B</span>型水环真空泵，一台工作，一台备用，抽采能力<span
lang=EN-US>140m3/min</span>。西翼采区抽采主管均采用Φ<span lang=EN-US>500mm</span>的聚乙烯瓦斯抽采管，<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>中底抽巷安设一趟Φ<span lang=EN-US>315mm</span>的聚乙烯瓦斯抽采管、一趟Φ<span
lang=EN-US>200mm</span>的聚乙烯瓦斯抽采管，<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下底抽巷安设一趟Φ<span
lang=EN-US>315mm</span>的聚乙烯瓦斯抽采管、一趟Φ<span lang=EN-US>200mm</span>的聚乙烯瓦斯抽采管，可用于对钻孔施工区域进行抽采。</span></a></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:28.0pt;
line-height:150%;text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体'>1.</span><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体'>巷道断面尺寸</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:150%;text-autospace:none'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体'>根据通风、运输、行人及安全间隙要求，结合煤巷掘进工作面顺槽受压变形的经验，<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷采用净宽×净高<span
lang=EN-US>=5000</span>×<span lang=EN-US>3000mm</span>的矩形断面，<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷采用净宽×净高<span
lang=EN-US>=3600</span>×<span lang=EN-US>2600mm</span>的矩形断面，<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>上巷采用净宽×净高<span
lang=EN-US>=4200</span>×<span lang=EN-US>3100mm</span>的矩形断面，切眼采用净宽×净高<span
lang=EN-US>=5400</span>×<span lang=EN-US>2600mm</span>的矩形断面。顺槽及切眼沿煤层顶底板掘进，当煤层厚度不够时破底施工。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:28.1pt;
line-height:150%;text-autospace:none'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
14.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体'>2.</span></b><b><span style='font-size:
14.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体'>巷道支护</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:28.1pt;
line-height:150%;text-autospace:none'><a name="_Toc465496492"><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体'>确定巷道支护形式</span></b></a></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:150%;text-autospace:none'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体'>根据临近巷道及钻孔揭露情况，<span lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span>回采范围二<sub><span
lang=EN-US>2</span></sub>煤直接顶为砂质泥岩，砂质泥岩</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体'>厚度<span lang=EN-US>2.47</span>～<span
lang=EN-US>2.59m</span>，平均厚度<span lang=EN-US>2.49m</span></span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体'>，基本顶为厚度<span
lang=EN-US>4.78</span>～<span lang=EN-US>5.28m</span>粉砂岩、<span lang=EN-US>2.07</span>～<span
lang=EN-US>16.14m</span>中砂岩，</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:
150%;font-family:宋体'>巷道顶板适合锚网带支护</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:宋体'>。根据矿井掘进巷道的矿压观察及支护经验，确定采用“锚网带<span lang=EN-US>+</span>锚索”联合支护。</span></p>

<p class=a align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:28.1pt'><b><span
style='font-family:宋体'>七、风量计算</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:23.5pt;layout-grid-mode:
char'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>1</span><span
