<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>4</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>、按工作人员数量计算</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:138.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>Q</span><sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>采</span></sub><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>=4N=4</span><span style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>×<span lang=EN-US>40=160</span>（<span lang=EN-US>m<sup>3</sup>/min</span>）</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>式中：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>N</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—工作面同时工作的最多人数，<span lang=EN-US>40</span>人；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>4</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—每人每分钟需新鲜风量，<span lang=EN-US>m<sup>3</sup></span>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>5</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>、风量验算</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:25.0pt'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>）</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>验算最小风量</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:96.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>Q</span><sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>采<span lang=EN-US>min</span></span></sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>≥<span lang=EN-US>60</span>×<span
lang=EN-US>V<sub>min</sub></span>×<span lang=EN-US>S<sub>max</sub>=60</span>×<span
lang=EN-US>0.25</span>×<span lang=EN-US>7.67=115.05m</span>&sup3;<span lang=EN-US>/min</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>式中：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>V<sub>min</sub></span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—采煤工作面允许的最低风速，为<span lang=EN-US>0.25m/s</span>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>Q</span><sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>采<span lang=EN-US>min</span></span></sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—采煤工作面允许的最小风量，<span lang=EN-US>m</span>&sup3;<span
lang=EN-US>/min</span>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>S<sub>max</sub></span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—工作面最大有效断面积，<span lang=EN-US>S<sub>max</sub>=</span>工作面最大控顶距×工作面实际采高×<span
lang=EN-US>70%=4.06</span>×<span lang=EN-US>2.7</span>×<span lang=EN-US>70%=7.67m</span>&sup2;。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（<span lang=EN-US>2</span>）验算最大风量：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:72.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>Q</span><sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>采<span lang=EN-US>max</span></span></sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>＜<span lang=EN-US>60</span>×<span
lang=EN-US>V<sub>max</sub></span>×<span lang=EN-US>S<sub>min</sub>=60</span>×<span
lang=EN-US>4.0</span>×<span lang=EN-US>6.54=1569.6m</span>&sup3;<span lang=EN-US>/min</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>式中：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>V<sub>max</sub></span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—采煤工作面允许的最高风速，为<span lang=EN-US>4m/s</span>；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>Q</span><sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>采<span lang=EN-US>max</span></span></sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—采煤工作面允许的最大风量，<span lang=EN-US>m</span>&sup3;<span
lang=EN-US>/min</span>；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>S<sub>min</sub></span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—工作面最小有效断面积，<span lang=EN-US>S<sub>min</sub>=</span>工作面最小控顶距×工作面实际采高×<span
lang=EN-US>70%=3.46</span>×<span lang=EN-US>2.7</span>×<span lang=EN-US>70%=6.54m</span>&sup2;。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（3）</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>按煤矿用防爆柴油动力装置机车功率验算风量</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:96.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>Q</span><sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>柴</span></sub><span style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>≥<span lang=EN-US>4</span>×<span lang=EN-US>N</span>×<span
lang=EN-US>P</span><sub>柴</sub>（<span lang=EN-US>m<sup>3</sup>/min</span>）<span
lang=EN-US>=4</span>×<span lang=EN-US>1</span>×<span lang=EN-US>149=596m</span>&sup3;<span
lang=EN-US>/min</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>式中：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>N</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—工作面顺槽最多运行防爆柴油动力装置机车的台数，<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>台；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>P</span><sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>柴</span></sub><span style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>—煤矿用防爆柴油动力装置机车的功率，<span lang=EN-US>149kW</span>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>6</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>、确定工作面实际需要风量</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:72.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>Q</span><sub><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>柴</span></sub><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>(596m</span><span style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&sup3;<span lang=EN-US>/min)</span>＜<span lang=EN-US>1151m</span>&sup3;<span
lang=EN-US>/min</span>＜<span lang=EN-US>Q</span><sub>采<span lang=EN-US>max</span></sub><span
lang=EN-US>(1569.6m</span>&sup3;<span lang=EN-US>/min)</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>回采期间需风量为<span lang=EN-US>1151m<sup>3</sup>/min</span>。</span></p>

