<p class=New style='text-indent:27.55pt;line-height:25.0pt'><a
name="_Toc410282994"><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>一、评判范围</span></b></a></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>1.</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>评判范围名称：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'> </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${evaluateUnit.evaluateunitname!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>2.</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>评判范围：</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'> </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${evaluateUnit.evaluateunitname!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（即<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷为<span
lang=EN-US>404G9</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>75m</span>至<span lang=EN-US>404G6</span>点内<span
lang=EN-US>29.4m</span>（评判范围：<span lang=EN-US>387.4m</span>），<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷为<span
lang=EN-US>404P7</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>45m</span>至<span lang=EN-US>404P2</span>点内<span
lang=EN-US>45.6m</span>（评判范围：<span lang=EN-US>359.8m</span>），及其对应的回采区域煤体），<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>综采工作面</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>Ⅰ</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>段预留超前<span
lang=EN-US>20m</span>已参与评判并取得批复本次评判只叙述不再重复评判</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>；</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>上部（即</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>2404</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>上巷为<span
lang=EN-US>404H10</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>101m</span>至<span lang=EN-US>404H3</span>点内<span
lang=EN-US>46m</span></span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（评判范围：<span
lang=EN-US>493.2m</span>），</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>2404</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>中巷为<span
lang=EN-US>404G9</span>点内<span lang=EN-US>75m</span>至<span lang=EN-US>404G5</span>点内<span
lang=EN-US>38.7m</span></span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（评判范围：<span
lang=EN-US>480.2m</span>），及其对应的回采区域煤体）。</span></p>

<p class=New style='text-indent:27.55pt;line-height:25.0pt'><a
name="_Toc410282995"><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>二、评判依据</span></b></a></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.25pt;line-height:25.0pt'><a
name="_Toc410282996"><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>1.</span></a><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>《煤矿安全规程》（</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>2022</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>版）</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt'> </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.25pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>2.</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>《防治煤与瓦斯突出细则》（</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>2019</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>年</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>10</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>月）</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.25pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>3.</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>《煤矿瓦斯抽采达标暂行规定》（</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>2011</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>年</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>12</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>月）</span></p>

<p class=New style='text-indent:27.55pt;line-height:25.0pt'><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>三、评判小组</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.25pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>顺和煤矿区域防突措施效果检验及瓦斯抽采达标评判小组机构如下：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.25pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>组</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp; </span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>长：矿长</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.25pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>副组长：总工程师</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.25pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>成</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp; </span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>员：防突矿长、通风副总、地测副总、采掘副总、安全副总及通风防突科、地测科、生产技术科、机电科、安检科、调度室等单位有关人员。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.25pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>顺和煤矿成立以矿长为组长的区域防突措施效果检验及瓦斯抽采达标评判小组，小组专业人员对</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'> </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${evaluateUnit.evaluateunitname!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>区域防突措施效果检验及瓦斯抽采达标评判报告进行了评审。</span></p>

<p class=New style='text-indent:27.55pt;line-height:25.0pt'><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>二、区域防突措施</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>1.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>防突措施钻孔布置要求</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'> </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${evaluateUnit.evaluateunitname!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（下部）</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>区域防突措施采用穿层钻孔<span lang=EN-US>+</span>顺层钻孔方式进行治理，分别在<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>中底抽巷、<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下底抽巷施工穿层钻孔、<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷、<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷施工顺层钻孔，穿层钻孔采用机械扩孔有效抽采半径（根据中国矿业大学出具的《顺和煤矿机械扩孔有效抽采半径考察研究测试报告》），原则上按照不大于机械扩孔有效抽采半径<span
lang=EN-US>2</span>倍布置（<span lang=EN-US>3</span>个月<span lang=EN-US>15m</span>），顺层钻孔采用顺层钻孔有效抽采半径（根据《顺和煤矿基于“流量衰减法”的顺层钻孔瓦斯抽放有效半径测试报告》），原则上按照不大于有效抽采半径布置（<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>个月<span lang=EN-US>2.6m</span>），<span lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span></span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（下部）</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>区域所有穿层钻孔均进行机械扩孔；穿层钻孔<span lang=EN-US>+</span>顺层钻孔控制<span
lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span>区域。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>2.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>防突措施钻孔设计</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>根据中国矿业大学《顺和煤矿机械扩孔有效抽采半径考察研究测试报告》，机械扩孔有效抽采半径<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>个月<span lang=EN-US>7.4m</span>、<span lang=EN-US>2</span>个月<span
lang=EN-US>12m</span>、<span lang=EN-US>3</span>个月<span lang=EN-US>15m</span>，<span
lang=EN-US>6</span>个月<span lang=EN-US>18.2m</span>，<span lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span>Ⅱ段区域防突措施钻孔布置在<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>中底抽巷、<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下底抽巷，所有钻孔共计设计<span
lang=EN-US>192</span>个，其中<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>中底抽巷钻孔<span lang=EN-US>15m</span>一组，每组<span
lang=EN-US>4</span>个，<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下底抽巷钻孔<span lang=EN-US>15m</span>一组，每组<span
lang=EN-US>6</span>个（断层处钻孔进行加密，每组<span lang=EN-US>2</span>个），所有钻孔均进行机械扩孔，钻孔扩孔煤量不得低于<span
lang=EN-US>0.3m</span>&sup3;<span lang=EN-US>/m</span>；根据《顺和煤矿基于“流量衰减法”的顺层钻孔瓦斯抽放有效半径测试报告》，预抽期<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>个月时为<span lang=EN-US>2.6m</span>，预抽期<span lang=EN-US>2</span>个月时为<span
lang=EN-US>2.9m</span>，<span lang=EN-US>3</span>个月时为<span lang=EN-US>3.1m</span>，<span
lang=EN-US>6</span>个月时为<span lang=EN-US>3.5m</span>，<span lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span>Ⅱ段区域防突措施钻孔布置在<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷、<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷，所有钻孔共计设计<span
lang=EN-US>146</span>个，其中<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷钻孔间距<span lang=EN-US>3m</span>一个，<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷钻孔间距<span lang=EN-US>1.5m</span>一个，<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>中底抽巷设计钻孔进尺<span
lang=EN-US>5612.1m</span>，<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>下底抽巷设计钻孔进尺<span
lang=EN-US>9701.2m</span>；<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷设计钻孔进尺<span lang=EN-US>6440m</span>，<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷设计钻孔进尺<span lang=EN-US>9885m</span>，共计<span lang=EN-US>31638.3m</span>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>3．</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>防突措施钻孔实际施工情况</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>表<span lang=EN-US>7&nbsp; </span>区域防突措施钻孔（穿层<span
lang=EN-US>+</span>顺层）施工记录</span></p>

