style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（下部）</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>区域防突措施钻孔竣工图</span></p>

<p class=New style='text-indent:27.55pt;line-height:25.0pt'><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>三、区域防突措施效果检验</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>1.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>区域防突效果检验依</span><span style='font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>据</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>根据《防治煤与瓦斯突出细则》第五十八条规定要求，当实测残余瓦斯含量小于</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>8m<sup>3</sup>/t</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（构造带小于</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>6m</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>&sup3;</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>/t</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>）和瓦斯压力小于</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>0.74MPa</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>，且检验钻孔施工过程中没有喷孔、顶钻或其他动力现象时，则判定该区域为无突出危险。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>根据《河南省强化煤矿安全生产暂行规定》第三条要求，当实测残余瓦斯含量小于</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt'>6m<sup>3</sup>/t</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>和瓦斯压力小于</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt'>0.6MPa</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:
宋体'>，且检验钻孔施工过程中没有喷孔、顶钻或其他动力现象时，经连续区域验证参数不超标，且无异常情况后，方</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>可在安全防护措施到位的情况下保留验证超前距回采。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>2.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>测点布置依据</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>依据《防治煤与瓦斯突出细则》第七十二条、《煤矿瓦斯抽采达标暂行规定》第二十六条：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>对预抽回采区煤层瓦斯区域防突措施进行检验时，若回采区域宽度未超过<span
lang=EN-US>120m</span>，则沿采煤工作面推进方向每间隔<span lang=EN-US> 30</span>～<span
lang=EN-US>50m </span>至少布置<span lang=EN-US>2</span>个检验测试点，否则，应当应当沿采煤工作面推进方向每间隔<span
lang=EN-US>30</span>～<span lang=EN-US>50m </span>至少布置<span lang=EN-US>3</span>个检验测试点，且检验测试点距离回采巷道两帮大于<span
lang=EN-US>20m</span>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>同时《防治煤与瓦斯突出细则》第七十二条规定：各检验测试点应当布置于所在钻孔密度较小、孔间距较大、预抽时间较短的位置，并尽可能远离各预抽瓦斯钻孔或者尽可能与周围预抽瓦斯钻孔保持等距离，避开采掘巷道的排放范围和工作面的预抽超前距。地质构造复杂区域适当增加检验测试点。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>附图<span lang=EN-US>4</span>：<span
lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span></span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（下部）</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>区域防突措施效果检验钻孔设计图</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>3.</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'> </span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>防突措施效果检验钻孔实际施工情况</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（下部）</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>斜长超过<span lang=EN-US>120m</span>，措施效果检验钻孔在布置时沿工作面推进方向每间隔<span
lang=EN-US>30</span>～<span lang=EN-US>50m</span>至少布置<span lang=EN-US>3</span>个测点。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>本次效果检验钻孔在<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>中底抽巷、<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>下底抽巷施工，按照沿工作面推进方向每间隔<span lang=EN-US>30</span>～<span
lang=EN-US>50m </span>至少布置<span lang=EN-US>3</span>个检验测试点的要求，共计施工区域防突措施效果检验钻孔<span
lang=EN-US>64</span>个；取样钻孔兼做测压钻孔，测定煤层残余瓦斯压力。<span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.5pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>附图<span lang=EN-US>5</span>：<span
lang=EN-US>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>（下部）</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>区域防突措施效果检验钻孔竣工图</span></p>

<p class=New style='text-indent:27.55pt;line-height:25.0pt'><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体'>四、区域验证</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>${workFace.workingfacename!""}</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>（下部）</span><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体'>回采期间采用复合指标法进行连续区域验证。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>1.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>验证钻孔布置：钻孔应尽量布置在软分层中，钻孔尽可能位于煤层中部，垂直于煤壁施工，倾角与采面推进一致。钻孔直径为<span
lang=EN-US>42mm</span>，孔间距<span lang=EN-US>10m</span>～<span lang=EN-US>15m</span>，孔深<span
lang=EN-US>5m</span>～<span lang=EN-US>10m</span>。钻孔沿工作面从<span lang=EN-US>2404</span>中巷到<span
lang=EN-US>2404</span>下巷上帮<span lang=EN-US>10m</span>范围内布置，在构造及瓦斯异常带附近加密布孔，孔间距控制在<span
lang=EN-US>5m</span>以内。验证孔尽量布置在软分层和靠近构造处，若钻孔施工不到位须调整钻孔倾角后补孔。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:25.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>2.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>区域验证时，钻孔从第<span lang=EN-US>2m</span>深度开始，每钻进<span
lang=EN-US>1m</span>测定该<span lang=EN-US>1m</span>段的全部钻屑量<span lang=EN-US>S</span>，并在暂停钻进后<span
lang=EN-US>2min</span>内测定钻孔瓦斯涌出初速度<span lang=EN-US>q</span>，测量室长度为<span
lang=EN-US>1m</span>，只有当实测到的指标<span lang=EN-US>q</span>的所有测定值小于<span
lang=EN-US>4.9L/min</span>，指标<span lang=EN-US>S</span>的测定值小于<span lang=EN-US>5.73kg/m</span>，并且无瓦斯动力现象或突出预兆时，则该区域验证结果为无突出危险。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:25.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>3.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>进行区域验证时，严禁与参数验证无关的工作同时进行。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:25.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>4.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>过地质构造、进行回采作业及打钻期间出现各种现象及处理要求：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:25.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>(1)</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>煤层的构造破坏带，包括断层、剧烈褶曲、火成岩侵入等。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>(2)</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>煤层赋存条件急剧变化。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>(3)</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>采掘应力叠加。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>(4)</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>工作面出现喷孔、顶钻等；</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>(5)</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>工作面出现明显的突出预兆。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>当出现上述第<span lang=EN-US>(4)</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>(5)</span>情况时，应判定该工作面为突出危险工作面；立即实施或补充区域防突措施，当有上述第<span lang=EN-US>(1)</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>(2)</span>、<span lang=EN-US>(3)</span>情况时，除已实施了工作面防突措施的以外，应视为突出危险工作面并实施相关措施。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>5.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>过断层期间进行区域验证时，必须在断层面附近<span lang=EN-US>5m</span>范围内至少布置一个验证孔，若在打眼过程中未打到设计深度遇见岩石的，调整验证孔施工位置和角度，但距临近验证孔不得超过<span
lang=EN-US>15m</span>，直至能够打至设计深度为止。</span></p>

<p class=MsoBodyTextFirstIndent2 style='margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>6.</span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体'>验证结束后验证人员要及时汇报区域验证情况，验证时保留的预测孔超前距不得小于<span
lang=EN-US>2m</span>。</span></p>

